  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to explore the experiences and needs of patients with a
      high-grade glioma and their caregivers. Semi-structured interviews with patients and
      caregivers will be conducted and analysed using Grounded-Theory approach.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
